This paper deals with covert communication in wireless networks, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network security (cs.CR). The use of relays and multi-hop routing also involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and multimedia systems (cs.MM). Finally, the development of efficient algorithms for finding optimal paths involves systems and control (cs.SY).
